Class Participant

java.lang.Object
ru.nsu.g.solovev5.m.task112.participants.Participant
Direct Known Subclasses:
Dealer, Player
public abstract class Participant extends Object
Abstract class represents a participant. Provides functionality for interacting with cards, managing wins count.
